# The Vercel web build only needs the gym-app/ source + root vercel.json; it runs
# its own `npm install` + `vite build`. Excluding these keeps the upload under
# Vercel's 15k-file limit (the native projects + node_modules blew past it and
# forced a --archive=tgz workaround on the first deploy).
node_modules
dist
ios
android
.git
*.log
